Name: Lord You're Worthy
ChorusText:
LORD YOU’RE WORTHY
LORD YOU’RE WORTHY,
WORTHY TO BE PRAISED
WE EXALT YOU FOR YOUR LOVE AND GRACE
HALLELUJAH FOR OUR SAVIOUR REIGNS
LORD WE BLESS YOUR HOLY NAME
ON HIGH – WE LIFT YOU UP
AS WE SING YOUR PRAISE
LORD WE MAGNIFY YOUR NAME
TO JESUS CHRIST THE CRUCIFIED
BE ALL GLORY FOR EVER MORE
